{"tid":1822642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於近日有會員提出影大頭事宜","createTime":"2020-01-13T05:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T05:51:46.000Z","uid":73959,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a18bbb69b8db7ab3140dfaa256973837caab57b9","tid":1822642,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"基於<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰、不屈毛</span></span>原則下：<br />\n<br />\n我本人(不代表全連登仔)<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不反對但亦非支持</span></span>影大頭之行為。<br />\n<br />\n因為我明白，每個人對場運動付出都有一定嘅限度。如果<strong>你嘅能力只係能夠企喺藍店前影人大頭，我絕對體諒</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n同時間，希望你可以早日進修提升自己，做一啲對埋運動更有幫助嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283b5094efa60d9ee4c8902ea5ce45e260f7f520","tid":1822642,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0965c26ce2e590b8d10a2c7230afa12fbf91ea","tid":1822642,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"我不反對喇 咪再話我阻膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾個人mon唔住全港九藍店㗎喎，洗唔洗幫你搞個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和你影</span>？<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞計藍店定紅店？二百幾間分店至少要幾百個手足先得<br />\n<br />\n下面開放討論！"},{"pid":"788128985693d6782e0457e8e3076bbcdade8eb0","tid":1822642,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"分化post 拉"},{"pid":"cc9db5e0007de9a1372f1e07568ac0c6593292a2","tid":1822642,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"我屌哂你哋老母 係咪光復左香港 五大訴求達到左啦？ 做咩成個熱門都係食玩膠post？ 如果呢個post上唔到熱門 冇哂行動post 我正式宣布呢個運動真係玩完 連登已死 連我個淺藍老母都問啲暴徒係咪搞完事 外國戰線著哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一句<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a4b12871f91285722ae33c